#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.237"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.237:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.237:0.2"
msgid "24. Kammavagga"
msgstr "24. Deeds"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.237:0.3"
msgid "237. Ariyamaggasutta"
msgstr "237. The Noble Path"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.237:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, kammāni mayā sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā paveditāni."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I declare these four kinds of deeds, having realized them with "
"my own insight."

msgctxt "an4.237:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

#. </p><ol><li>
msgctxt "an4.237:1.3"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, kammaṃ kaṇhaṃ kaṇhavipākaṃ;"
msgstr "There are dark deeds with dark results;"

#. </li><li>
msgctxt "an4.237:1.4"
msgid "atthi, bhikkhave, kammaṃ sukkaṃ sukkavipākaṃ;"
msgstr "bright deeds with bright results;"

#. </li><li>
msgctxt "an4.237:1.5"
msgid "atthi, bhikkhave, kammaṃ kaṇhasukkaṃ kaṇhasukkavipākaṃ;"
msgstr "dark and bright deeds with dark and bright results; and"

#. </li><li>
msgctxt "an4.237:1.6"
msgid ""
"atthi, bhikkhave, kammaṃ akaṇhaasukkaṃ akaṇhaasukkavipākaṃ kammakkhayāya "
"saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"neither dark nor bright deeds with neither dark nor bright results, which "
"lead to the ending of deeds."

#. </li></ol><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.237:2.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, kammaṃ kaṇhaṃ kaṇhavipākaṃ?"
msgstr "And what are dark deeds with dark results?"

msgctxt "an4.237:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco sabyābajjhaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti … pe … "
"idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kammaṃ kaṇhaṃ kaṇhavipākaṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when someone makes hurtful choices by way of body, speech, and mind. "
"These are called dark deeds with dark results."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.236"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.237:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, kammaṃ sukkaṃ sukkavipākaṃ?"
msgstr "And what are bright deeds with bright results?"

msgctxt "an4.237:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco abyābajjhaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti … pe … idaṃ "
"vuccati, bhikkhave, kammaṃ sukkaṃ sukkavipākaṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when someone makes pleasing choices by way of body, speech, and mind. "
"These are called bright deeds with bright results."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.237:4.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, kammaṃ kaṇhasukkaṃ kaṇhasukkavipākaṃ?"
msgstr "And what are dark and bright deeds with dark and bright results?"

msgctxt "an4.237:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco sabyābajjhampi abyābajjhampi kāyasaṅkhāraṃ "
"abhisaṅkharoti … pe … idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kammaṃ kaṇhasukkaṃ "
"kaṇhasukkavipākaṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when someone makes both hurtful and pleasing choices by way of body, "
"speech, and mind. These are called dark and bright deeds with dark and "
"bright results."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.237:5.1"
msgid ""
"Katamañca, bhikkhave, kammaṃ akaṇhaasukkaṃ akaṇhaasukkavipākaṃ kammakkhayāya "
"saṃvattati?"
msgstr ""
"And what are neither dark nor bright deeds with neither dark nor bright "
"results, which lead to the ending of deeds?"

msgctxt "an4.237:5.2"
msgid "Sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"Right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "an4.237:5.3"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kammaṃ akaṇhaasukkaṃ akaṇhaasukkavipākaṃ "
"kammakkhayāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"These are called neither dark nor bright deeds with neither dark nor bright "
"results, which lead to the ending of deeds."

msgctxt "an4.237:5.4"
msgid ""
"Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri kammāni mayā sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"paveditānī”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the four kinds of deeds that I declare, having realized them with "
"my own insight.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.237:5.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
